    <briefdescription>
<para>UART driver — buffered I/O and formatted output. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides interrupt-driven buffered UART on top of the port layer. Each UART instance gets a TX and RX ring buffer. The buffer sizes are configurable in syn_config.h. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
